{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01PZPu3SFLu7vJ4wsPDGRnuC","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tests pass. Here's a summary of the changes:\n\n**Root cause:** Two bugs caused the task to show as \"succeeded\" despite a failed host workflow:\n\n1. **`internal/host/loop.go:runPhased()`** — The finalize result was discarded (`_`), and only `mainResult.State` was sent to the completions channel. A succeeded develop step would override a failed finalize (merge) step.\n\n2. **`internal/domain/run.go:TaskAggregateStatus()`** — Among terminal runs, it picked the most recently *started* run. Since child container runs always start after their parent host run, a succeeded container run would override a failed host run in the web UI.\n\n**Fixes:**\n\n- **`internal/domain/run.go`**: Added `WorseState(a, b RunState)` helper that returns the more severe of two terminal states (failed > cancelled > succeeded). Updated `TaskAggregateStatus` to prefer the most recently started *host* run's state among terminal runs, since host runs represent the full attempt including finalize. Falls back to most-recent for non-host runs.\n\n- **`internal/host/loop.go`**: Changed `runPhased()` to compute the worst of `mainResult.State` and finalize's outcome before sending to the completions channel.\n\n**Tests added:**\n- `TestWorseState` — 6 cases covering all severity comparisons\n- 4 new `TestTaskAggregateStatus` cases for host-run-vs-child scenarios\n- `TestPhaseLoop_FinalizeFailureOverridesMainSuccess` and `TestPhaseLoop_FinalizeErrorOverridesMainSuccess`\n- `TestRunsList_HostRunFailedOverridesChildSuccess` — end-to-end web handler test\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":353,"cache_read_input_tokens":68149,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":353},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b8cb8c5e-8c4d-4714-8529-015666123eea","uuid":"5dc9f5b6-f37a-43df-b44f-009984fd049f"}
